The pin connections between the Pi, the motor driver, the ultrasound sensors and the motors :

Pi and MotorDriver(L298N):
Pi Pin  |  Motor Driver
2       |   5v pin
6       |   GND pin
7       |   IN4
11      |   IN3
13      |   IN2
15      |   IN1

Pi and Front Sensor(HC-SR04)
18      |    ECHO
16      |    TRIG

Pi and Right Sensor(HC-SR04)
29      |    TRIG
31      |    ECHO

NOTE : I've not included the motor connections or the GND and Vcc connections for the Sensors, and the Driver.
